Author: Silicat1510
Title: [ANN]🔥🔥 KRYLL.IO -Automated crypto trading strategies made simple 🔥🔥
Body: About Kryll.io Since 2009, Bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies enjoyed a phenomenal growth in terms of public interest and valuation. Holding investors, professional traders and hobbyists all bene ted in their own ways from the amazing opportunities granted by this brave new world. Nevertheless the trading game requires time, technical knowledge, analytical skills, discipline and proficiency using professional tools in order to achieve true success. Crypto traders without all of this missed opportunities or lost a chunk of their assets in the last few years.  Now that the Kryll.io platform enters the game, this is changing.  Kryll.io is your first intuitive platform to define powerful crypto trading strategies through a simple drag’n’drop editor. With our Wysiwyt™ (What You See Is What You Trade) flow-based technology you are now able to build from basic to advanced automated trading systems in an intuitive way, no dev skills needed anymore!  Kryll.io provides logical operators, markets indicators, value triggers, enhanced technical analysis, media opinion mining and deep-learning predictions; all this will help your to create automated winning strategies. Benchmark your strategies through real-time sandboxes and massive Kryll.io back-testing capabilities, share with the community, enjoy user-generated content… the revolution is here, don’t trade your life away!

Body: Hi there, I've read the White Paper, and I found something I don't understand in the "legal" section.   Here it is: "Sales restrictions The participation in the ICO is strictly reserved for natural or legal persons acting within the scope of their professional activities. Especially, the professional purchaser claims to have a good knowledge of blockchain technologies and cryptocurrency. Any natural person acting on a non-professional basis as a simple consumer within the meaning of EU Directive 2011/83/EU relating to consumer rights is excluded from the ICO. It is the responsibility of each purchaser to determine its non-professional status and, in doing so, to refrain from participating in any way in the ICO."  Is it commonplace to find that kind of assertion in a White Paper ? Does that mean that every participant in the ICO would be seen, according to law, as a professional ?

Author: BScrk
Title: [ANN]🔥🔥 KRYLL.IO -Automated crypto trading strategies made simple 🔥🔥
Body: The real goal of the project is to provide a simple way to create your own automated strategies (trading / alerts / analytics / telegram signals...) in a simple & intuitive way in order to free time & enjoy your life.  Indeed, Kryll.io will provide a drag’n’drop strategy editor (no dev skills needed anymore) to create your triggers & actions based trading strategies (or alerts...). With kryll.io flows editor, you'll be able to visually describes the confluence of signals, operators and relevant data determining a particular strategy.  Like LEGO(R) building system, Kryll.io will provide differents types of blocks to create your automat :  - Market Trends : like usual trend analysis, technical data analysis, studies and modeling units, ecc...)  - Trading actions : like buy, sell, split amount into subsets, loop, stop ecc...)  - Signals : coming from professional traders, qualified Telegram channels, social network semantic analyses, ecc...)  - Operators : to organize data feeds and signal interactions (eg: IF the market is up AND “BTC” is receiving positive feedback on Twitter THEN do this...)  - Notifications : to keep you informed of a strategy’s status (this could be a text message, email or smart notification)  I encourage you to read the whitepaper to learn more about this. We'll also release some videos explaining the concept soon.

Title: [ANN]🔥🔥 KRYLL.IO -Automated crypto trading strategies made simple 🔥🔥
Body: Hi, thanks for the interest and question. We've been trading cryptos (for ourselves and our company) for several years, so yes indeed we take security to the upmost consideration, or we wouldn't be able to fund the project right now . We've lost a few BTC on a famous mining platform a few months ago . About the IT team, Fabien is our back-office expert, he's been working on web services (video, social, etc ...) for like forever and he's had to secure those services that contained either copyrighted or sensitive data. Also we have in our board of advisors (who are people we intend to work with on a regular basis after the sale) Clement who's managing high availability servers (for an audience measurement company) on a day to day basis. As a side note, because Luca (CEO) is a security freak, we intend to implement a regular external security audit (read get a hacker team to test the platform) of all our systems to make sure everything is and stays fine.  Hope this helps

Author: kryll
Title: [ANN]🔥🔥 KRYLL.IO -Automated crypto trading strategies made simple 🔥🔥
Body: Website | Whitepaper | Twitter | Telegram | Facebook  Introduction   Kryll.io is the ultimate platform for crypto traders. Use the most advanced trading tools and strategies, as well as benefit from the community’s hive-mind to get the best returns within cryptocurrency markets.  The platform provides intuitive ways to create your own trading strategies that can be set to execute automatically. Through a What You See Is What You Trade™ interface you can design trading strategies making use of the industry’s most powerful tools and safely test them with backtesting and sandboxing.  Kryll provides several tools to build and test your strategies   Visual flow-based construction (no dev skills needed)  Huge "block-set" to create from basic to complex trading behaviours.  Technical Analysis blocks (RSI, MACD, Ichimoku, MAs ... )  Detailled graphics with TradingView™ Charts integration.  Free Live simulation and backtesting.  More than 8 months market data history to the minute.  But also   Kryll Marketplace where you can rent your strategies or strategies from other traders.  Community channel to exchange ideas, strategies tips and development polls to build together the future of trading!  Once your tools prove their worth you can set them to live-trade on your behalf, taking the right positions at the right time, as if you were following the markets 24/7.  On Kryll.io you can also rent out your very own winning strategies to help fellow traders be more successful. You will be rewarded with passive income for sharing your strategies.           You can follow us on Twitter @kryll_io for more updates. Or join our Telegram channel.
